<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="background-color: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span></span><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">I’m still struggling to reach you since you were referred to us by&nbsp;</span></font>Powered Now<font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.</span></font><br><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">It’s likely you are looking at lots of different providers for your business insurance policy. So, here are the reasons why the team at Kingsbridge stand out from our competitors:</span></font></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><ul style="font-size: 12pt;"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Real people, real support:&nbsp;</b>quick access to dedicated UK-based insurance specialists.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>UK-based claims centre:&nbsp;</b>rapid, responsive claims processing managed by an in-house claims team.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>There when you need them:</b>&nbsp;strong history of fair, fast, and hassle-free claims processing.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Tailored industry expertise:</b>&nbsp;cover specifically built for contractors, freelancers, and small business owners.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>No hidden fees:&nbsp;</b>transparent pricing with no unexpected costs.</font></li></ul><p class="MsoNormal"><font style="font-size: 12pt;">Let’s catch up on the phone so I can make sure I provide you with the best policy for you at the best price.&nbsp;<b><a href="https://calendly.com/d/cnbd-zyn-qwh/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back-powered-now">Book a call with me</a></b>.<br><br></font><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">As a client of&nbsp;</b><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Powered Now</b></font><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">, you are entitled to a discount of 10% on our standard business insurance package.</b></span><font style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><br>Alternatively, contact me on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>. Our office is open 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you soon!<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
